*Onu* košulju sam kupio pre nekoliko dana. (I bought that shirt a few days ago.)

*Onu* pticu sam video u parku. (I saw that bird in the park.)

*Onu* reč je teško zapamtiti. (It's hard to remember that word.)

*Onoj* devojci je bilo žao što je propustila događaj. (That girl was sorry she missed the event.)

*Onim* lekom su kod nje uspeli da ispravi problem. (They managed to fix the problem with that medicine.)

*Onima* koji nisu bili tu nije bilo jasno šta se desilo. (Those who weren't there didn't understand what happened.)